The stats of the advanced magic manual.<br>
<br>
Advanced Magic Manual<br>
Slot: RANGE SECONDARY<br>
AC: 15<br>
WIS: 12 INT 12 HP 35 MANA 35<br>
recc 55<br>
1.0 wt small<br>
all/all<br>
<br>
And after turning it in...<br>
<br>
He sends you to Tenada Jeried who asks you to bring him all three advanced manuals and a &quot;Hope Stone&quot; which &quot;currently lies somewhere in the elemental planes.&quot;<br>
