<br>
After that you have the Planar Manual, buy a HGS in the bazaar. On SoRo they are sold for about 100 PP nowadays. Make sure to store it BEHIND your regular food, return to PoK, and hand BOTH, Manual and HGS to Acomar Lothwol .<br>
<br>
He stands in the between 2 other peeps in the Bridge Tower in the Good Section of PoK.<br>
<br>
I have this item on all my caster, and did it at lvl 20. It is very easy assuming you have the cash to get the HGS.<br>
<br>
Here the reversed walkthrough:<br>
<br>
&quot;I combined information from Sage Dargadin's Post (with Rozwel's corretion) and combined information Luethar's Coords to Fed Ex post and information from Scholar Joeracke's post.  I did a little reworking for clarity and checked with my own experience from walking through the quest and came up with the following: <br>
<br>
Starting from the book and working back to Willamina: <br>
<br>
Book: -100, +1000, +68 (so you know which floor) <br>
next to Sir Geravaldi <br>
<br>
Agrakath: -552, +1216, -124 Erudite <br>
NW most corner of evil area <br>
<br>
Caden: -342, +751, -91 Gnome <br>
SE corner of the group of buildings you see as you enter the Inner Ring of PoK comming from Agrakath. <br>
<br>
Boiron: +31, +322, -123 Dwarf <br>
(NE of Caden) outside and west side of building by Neutral Part in the Inner Ring. <br>
<br>
Elisha: +391, +944, -91 Human <br>
From Boiron, follow the Inner ring NW toward the north side of town. She is in the first door on the right after you climb the stairs to the buildings. <br>
<br>
Narik: +446, +146, -156 Human <br>
In the caster building which is directly to left of Nexus Portal. <br>
<br>
Onirelin: -651, +1051, -123 Dark Elf <br>
In the building with the ramp up to the library in evil area. He is to the right of the door as you enter the building. <br>
<br>
Cador: +700, +100, -155 <br>
SE most building of the good part of town. <br>
<br>
Mirao: -90, -211, -155 <br>
Building in the middle of Neutral Area east of the library ramp building and west of PoT portal <br>
<br>
Bolcen: +683, +951, -123 <br>
Good part of town, he's in the building that leads to the archway to the lilbrary (Acomar Lothwol is in the same building, to Bolcen's right)<br>
<br>
Willamina: -428, +1148, -124 <br>
Sitting under a tree in the SW part of Inner town (south of Library north of evil section). <br>
<br>
PS...if you're doing this quest for experience like I was ...DON'T ...I got a blue or less for my level 9 warrior from doing this. <br>
